# Nexus-Cloud Secret Configuration Template
# Upload this JSON object to AWS Secrets Manager as 'nexus-cloud/ai-api-keys'

# JSON Structure:
# {
#   "ANTHROPIC_API_KEY": "sk-ant-...",
#   "OPENAI_API_KEY": "sk-...",
#   "GEMINI_API_KEY": "...",
#   "SUBSCRIPTION_MODE": "true" 
# }

# Instructions:
# 1. Use the AWS Console or CLI to create the secret.
# 2. Key names must match the script retrieval logic in common_setup.sh.
# 3. If SUBSCRIPTION_MODE is true, the setup script will prioritize OAuth/Device flow for subscription limits.
